title: PETBAKERY NATURAL PET FOOD - Beef & Fish
descriptions: We combine the nutrition and taste of fresh, raw food and put it through a gentle freeze drying process which protects all the natural enzymes and nutrients, so none of the wholesome goodness is cooked out.

To use PETBAKERY NATURAL PET FOOD can be served as dry or re-hydrated by adding fresh water. If your cat does not drink plenty of water at mealtime, we recommend re-hydrating equal parts food to water.
That's also a good way to use PETBAKERY NATURAL PET FOOD simply mix with your cat’s current diet for a daily nutrient boost.
Your cat will go crazy over the taste of PETBAKERY NATURAL PET FOOD.
ingredients: Beef, Mackeral, Beef heart, Beef liver, Beef kidney, Hoki, Kelp, New Zealand green mussel
